data.description: Located twenty minutes from Walla Walla and just a half hour from the Tri-Cities this three-bedroom two two-bath home features a large city lot with a detached two-car garage. This home is an affordable option for any homeowner in South Eastern Washington. Come see this home for yourself and enjoy the peace and quiet this yard and community have to offer.
